Description:
Designer Docklands Living with Inspired Views
Stunning with remarkable views of Victoria Harbour, Marvel Stadium, and the iconic CBD, this two bedroom, two bathroom Palladio apartment with a design by renowned architects Fender Katsalidis is blissful NewQuay Precinct living.
You’ll never get sick of the amazing water and CBD views which are best enjoyed from the main balcony, which is accessed via the living and meals zone and is a sensational space for weekend dinners and drinks which will become part of your weekly routine. There are also two additional balconies with views which each have excellent privacy and are located off the bedrooms.
A stone-featured kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and timber cabinetry. The master bedroom has excellent built-in robe storage, a study nook, and a striking ensuite, while the 2nd bedroom also comes with a BIR. Further living highlights include an attractive bathroom, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a health club with rooftop pool, gym, and private function area.
Moments to restaurants including Oscar’s Table, Renzo’s Bar Café Italiano, and Fish Bar, IGA supermarket, The District Docklands, and the 30, 70, and 86 trams. This stylish Palladio apartment is calling your name, so don’t miss out on this terrific opportunity!
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.
Insights: 803/15 Caravel Lane, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2019 and 275 other 2 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Contemporary Marina Tower living with park views
A genuine modern marvel which can be found in the immaculate ‘Marina Tower’ which has a reputation of delivering apartments of the highest quality, this one bedroom + study residence with park views is an impeccable Docklands retreat!
This apartment has an abundance of amazing quality in each and every room, and is ideal to take on as an investment or even owner-occupy. The carpeted living/meals zone has access out to an enclosed undercover balcony terrace which has green park vistas and is perfect for entertaining no matter the weather. The kitchen comes with superior stone as well as stainless steel appliances, with the practical design sure to be appreciated by home cooks.
The sizeable bedroom features a built-in robe and its own dedicated study area, while a flawless bathroom is the epitome of contemporary class. Other property features include a concealed laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, and secure intercom. Marina Tower facilities also include a lavish lobby lounge, library, private business centre, meeting rooms, cinema, lounge and billiard room, kitchen and dining area, rooftop pool, gym, and expansive deck.
Location wise, it doesn’t get much better than this. You’re opposite The District Docklands with great restaurants and entertainment, and close to Ron Barassi Snr Park, Marvel Stadium, IGA supermarket, waterside eateries, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and Docklands Drive trams.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing
Internal area
50m²

Description:
Spectacular Yarra’s Edge living
Sheer splendour and unrivalled panoramic vistas are the defining qualities of this stunning 3 bedroom Yarra’s Edge Apartment. An expansive 141sqm approx. of living space with jaw dropping 270 degree views from the CBD to Port Phillip Bay.
Comprising; entry foyer, huge living and dining zone opening to entertainers terrace, gourmet kitchen complete with stone benchtops and stainless steel appliances, central bathroom, All bedrooms with direct access to a balcony, while the main suite boasts huge walk in robe and spectacular ensuite.
Additional Features: Two secure car spaces, storage cage, ducted heating & cooling, separate laundry, video intercom entry, ground floor cafe and restaurant, resident access to REKDEK including, gym, indoor pool, spa and steam room.
Don’t miss this opportunity to immerse yourself in this highly sought after building and location.

Description:
YOU’LL BE WRAPPED TO CALL THIS HOME!
The 'Mosaic' is Docklands incredibly popular boutique low rise residential nine story complex. It has been built to the highest of standards and positioned to take full aspects of natural lighting and scenery, with dual aspects which allow beautiful landscapes. With only four apartments per floor and two on the ninth floor, this development offers a heightened level of exclusivity. Perfect for any owner occupier or investor!
Located on the 8th floor is this immaculate three bedroom apartment! The gourmet kitchen with stone bench tops and stainless steel appliances (Blanco) adjoins the spacious open plan living/dining area that spills out onto one of the two wide balconies which overlooks gorgeous park views. The spacious master bedroom has its own walk in robes and ensuite, while the other two bedrooms are fitted with built in robes and share a contemporary bathroom.
Conveniently situated close to restaurants, shopping, Marvel Stadium, Southern Cross Station and within a few minutes tram ride to Melbourne's CBD, this apartment has all that you need!
Other features include two secure car spaces, separate laundry facilities, reverse cycle air-con/heating units, ample storage space, security entrance, low body corporate fees and easy accessibility to the public transport nearby.

Description:
Experience Harbour and Garden views in the amazing Palladio
Be inspired by the outstanding contemporary flair, thoughtful layout and picturesque harbour & garden views that come with this 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom Palladio apartment situated right in the heart of the NewQuay Precinct.
This immaculate residence has a floorplan that allows for incredibly generous bedrooms and laid-back everyday living. There are dedicated spaces for lounge and dining, with the lounge opening out to a sizeable balcony where alfresco fun can be had as you soak in beautiful leafy views as well as the iconic Marvel Stadium.
The kitchen will be a haven for home gourmands and includes a breakfast bar and quality stainless steel appliances. The large master bedroom features a built-in robe and impressive ensuite, with the 2nd bedroom also boasting a BIR and private balcony. Other extras include a central bathroom, heating throughout, secure intercom, secure car space and access to a health club with rooftop pool, gym, and private function area.
Make the most of this stellar location which is just a short walk to brilliant surrounding attractions including the popular The District Docklands, terrific waterside restaurants, Marvel Stadium, IGA X-Press supermarket, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and trams on Harbour Esplanade and Docklands Drive.
To arrange an inspection, please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 or Lynn Lum on 0474 044 293

Description:
Beautiful Harbour Views and Impressive Contemporary Charm
From the striking internal detail all the way to the wonderful harbour views, this contemporary two bedroom apartment in the enviable Quays complex is your next stylish Docklands home.
A location on the 14th floor of this exclusive building and perfect south-easterly aspect sets you up for amazing water views which are best seen from the undercover balcony. This balcony space will get great workout all year round for alfresco dining! The spacious central lounge has everyday relaxing in mind, while a sizeable tiled meals zone adjoins the fantastic stone kitchen which comes with quality stainless steel Miele appliances.
Both bedrooms feature mirrored built-in robes including the master bedroom which has its own stylish private ensuite. Further embrace a gorgeous central bathroom with European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, and secure car space.
Access facilities including a Health Club with a pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge, and a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities. You’re positioned seconds to Marvel Stadium, fantastic restaurants and cafes including Woolshed, Mama Rumaan, and Mill & Bakery, The District Docklands, and local trams.

DIRECT WATERFRONT APARTMENT
Sophisticated waterfront luxury and breathtaking views of the Yarra River, Point Park, and the iconic Melbourne skyline make this one bedroom corner apartment a highly sought-after prize.
North-facing and located on the 9th floor of the stylish Yarra Point complex, this spacious pad measuring 76 sqm (approx.) showcases a dedicated lounge and meals areas, along with a designer kitchen featuring terrific storage and Miele appliances including a dishwasher.
The exceptional private balcony will be ideal in the warmer months for alfresco meals as you soak in the astonishing city and river vistas, while the bedroom (BIRs) neighbours a study nook and contemporary kitchen with large shower.
Further enjoying ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to building facilities including a gymnasium and heated pool, this retreat is in close proximity to South Wharf restaurants, DFO shopping, Etihad Stadium, CBD attractions, and public transport.

Description:
One of the finest offerings in the Yarra’s Edge precinct
With a refined and sophisticated edge that raises this apartment to a truly elite level, this pristine and ultra-spacious two bedroom, two bathroom residence has a wonderful position in the exclusive Yarra’s Edge precinct which is highly sought-after by owner-occupiers and investors.
From the unforgettable city views to interiors that dazzle with style, contemporary class, and superb space, this 25th floor apartment is irresistible. The incredible central living zone has a fantastic amount of room for you to move around in, with generous lounge and dining areas giving you amazing living options. In this main hub you can also find the state of the art kitchen which oozes elegance and boasts stunning bench and storage space along with stainless steel appliances. There is also a small meals area just off the kitchen.
A sizeable balcony is your best place to soak in the magnificent CBD and Yarra River vistas whether it be as you’re enjoying your first morning coffee or in the evening over a relaxed dinner. Both bedrooms share the views and have balcony access, with the master retreat further offering a delightful dual vanity ensuite.
Other property extras include built-in robes in both bedrooms, quality main bathroom, European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. The total living space of 128 sqm (approx.) is also sure to impress.
With a Yarra’s Edge precinct location, you’ll have access to some of the most appealing restaurants and bars in the Docklands which line the vibrant South Wharf Promenade, with this area also perfect for weekend shopping at the DFO complex. You’re also a short trip to Crown Casino, Southbank and Port Melbourne attractions, Victoria Harbour precinct, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station

Description:
Over 200 sqm of Conder brilliance
Offering 203 sqm (approx.) of exceptional living both inside and out, this contemporary and relaxed 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment with the addition of 2 secure car spaces is a rare Docklands find in the fantastic Conder residential complex.
The wonderful central lounge and dining zone offers an incredible amount of space, which is only matched by the enormous terrace. This magnificent area allows residents to enjoy alfresco dinners and drinks amongst friends and family, as well as being a dog lovers inner city paradise. This outdoor space also offers fantastic south-west views with glimpses of the harbour which are best seen from an elevated platform area.
A stone kitchen has functionality in mind and enjoys stainless steel Miele appliances plus a breakfast bar for meals on the go. Both bedrooms with built-in robes have access out to the balcony including the master bedroom which also comes with a stylish ensuite.
Other apartment highlights include a gorgeous central bathroom, separate laundry room, ducted heating and cooling, intercom entry, large storage cage and access to a pool, gym, and outdoor recreation area. In the NewQuay Precinct, you’re in close proximity to standout harbourside restaurants, Marvel Stadium, The District Docklands, and trams across the city and beyond.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
UNDER OFFER - 9th Floor Quays Retreat with Stunning City Views
East-facing which allows for direct views of the beautiful city skyline which is a sight to behold be it day or night, this open plan one bedroom apartment exudes stylish contemporary class and offers access to great facilities in the Quays residential complex.
This fantastic 9th floor apartment will have stunning appeal to both owner-occupiers and investors. Take advantage of relaxed living and meals zone, undercover balcony with exceptional city and leafy views below, stone kitchen with glass splashback and stainless steel Miele appliances, bedroom with built-in robe and views, classy designer bathroom, European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom and a secure car space.
The Quays offers some of the best residential facilities in Melbourne including access to a Health Club featuring a pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and yoga studio, as well as a Resident’s Club with library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room and cinema lounge. There is also a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
Love the surrounding NewQuay precinct attractions which include the popular The District Docklands, restaurants including Woolshed, Cargo, Wok on the Dock and Lotus Chinese Restaurant, Marvel Stadium, IGA X-Press supermarket and trams on Harbour Esplanade and Docklands Drive.

Description:
LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!
Meticulous fully-furnished apartment in the Flinders Wharf building.
With sweeping views up the Yarra River, sitting directly opposite the Melbourne Exhibition Centre, and amongst the bustling and vibrant bars and restaurants of South Wharf, is this fully furnished apartment.
With two bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an open living area, this recently updated apartment offers the keen investor the best of all options – either move right in and enjoy, rent it out to a long-term tenant, or continue it as a short-stay option, but having personal access when you need.
Currently managed on-site for short stays, the apartment is maintained in meticulous order and provides the current owners a better rental return than a permanent tenant whilst allowing them access to enjoy all Melbourne has to offer.
Step from the front door of the building directly onto the South Wharf boardwalk, and you are within an easy stroll to the DFO, Casino, Southbank, South Melbourne Markets, city centre, Etihad and the free city tram circuit.
Tastefully furnished in a modern contemporary style, the apartment has a King bed (in the master suite) and a Queen bed (in the guest room), with both able to be split into single bed options. The apartment is fully equipped with new stainless steel fridge and dishwasher, washer/drier, Smart TV, leather sofas and all kitchen requirements.
The apartment comes with a secure parking bay inside the building.
This is a rare opportunity to purchase a walk-in/walk-out apartment in one of Melbourne’s most sought-after buildings. Building amenities include gym, swimming pool, sauna and spa.
The current owners are only selling now due to relocating interstate and not using the apartment as often as originally anticipated. This is a private sale.
Contact Jody Elliott on 0419168250 to arrange a private viewing.

Description:
Prestigious Living over two levels with captivating Marina and City views
Graced with a coveted corner position allowing for remarkable views of the vibrant CBD and Victoria Harbour, this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom apartment over two levels is the pinnacle of stylish, elegant, and relaxed Docklands living.
This impressive retreat starts with a ground level highlighted by an open living and dining zone adjoined by the stone kitchen with stainless steel appliances, while a spacious balcony off the living zone, and another entertainer sized 2nd balcony off the master bedroom (with WIR and ensuite), offers a wealth of entertaining options.
Upstairs, two bedrooms both with BIRs are separated by the sleek bathroom, while a 3rd balcony can be accessed from the hallway or one of the bedrooms. Other features include a generous laundry room, ducted heat/cool, intercom entry, 2 car spaces and storage cage located on the same level just meters from your front door, as well as direct access to facilities including heated pool and gym.
Near Harbour Town Shopping Centre, NewQuay Promenade, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Etihad Stadium, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 or Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
An elite corner residence with gorgeous park views
From the exceptional internal space to a tremendous corner position which allows for wonderful natural light and views of the neighbouring Docklands Park and Marvel Stadium, this elite two bedroom, two bathroom apartment is a modern winner in the Watergate complex.
Be immediately impressed by the bright floor-to-ceiling windows and stunning natural light found in the large central living and dining zone, which is includes a sleek kitchen with dark elegant cabinetry, amazing bench space, and quality stainless steel appliances. This main hub also has access out to the north-facing balcony which will be a delight for alfresco entertaining!
A master bedroom has entry out to its own balcony area and also includes a study nook, dual mirrored built-in robes, and stylish ensuite. Other terrific property features include a 2nd bedroom with BIR, elegant two-way bathroom with laundry facilities, central heating and cooling, intercom entry, secure car space, and access to facilities including an onsite pool, sauna, and gym.
The Watergate complex sits in a great position close to all the attractions of both the Victoria Harbour and Batman’s Hill precincts. You’re close to The Hub @ Docklands, outdoor sporting facilities, an array of restaurants and cafes, Harbour Esplanade trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Myles Johansson on 0448 031 716 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Enjoy the stunning water views and watching fireworks at home
Enjoy uninterrupted views of the Docklands Waterfront, Melbourne CBD and Port Phillip Bay from every room through the floor to ceiling windows.
This exceptional north east facing three bedrooms apartment features bedrooms with ample built in robes space, central open plan living areas with plenty of storages, contemporary kitchen with Miele stainless steel appliances and Fisher & Paykel dishwasher. 3 Modern bathrooms (2 ensuites), 2 private winter balconies, intercom, building security, heating/cooling systems and 2 car spaces on title.
Marina Tower - the place to be for shopping, dining, entertainment, access to CBD (free tram zone), fantastic view and lifestyle! The District across the road is a buzzing place with new Hoyts cinema opening in the future and food trucks scene. New Quay will provide you with contemporary dining experience and Docklands Sunday Market.
Marina Tower has world class resort feel facilities:
- Ground level - Library, Lounge, Gallery Space, Business Centre, Conference rooms
- Mezzanine level - Private Cinema, Billiard Room and Private Dining and Kitchen
- Level 7 - Fully equipped gymnasium & 25m lap pool, garden area & sun lounge chairs and kabanas to enjoy Melbourne's great views
